该节点涉及的全局状态如下：
  - orders (read_write): Dict mapping order_id to {items, payment, address, status, created_at}
  - inventory (read_write): Dict mapping product_id to {stock_count, reserved_count, price}
  - payments (read_write): Dict mapping payment_id to {order_id, amount, method, status}

请说明你对每个全局变量的理解。它的数据结构是什么？读写操作分别在什么场景下发生？
